{
  "texts": [
    "While we carefully put together a benchmark for evaluation, it's important to note that there might be biases present that may show up in evaluations.",
    "Furthermore, we employed different sampling techniques to avoid evaluation bias for different classes.",
    "Although we tried our best to evaluate the models consistently, the models are sensitive to prompt wordings.",
    "For the same prompts too, the models are not consistent with the answers when changed the order of options as mentioned in PPA.",
    "Therefore there can be slight variations in the performances when trying to reproduce the results."
  ]
}